ENTRY       EC 3.2.1.59                 Enzyme
NAME        glucan endo-1,3-alpha-glucosidase;
            endo-1,3-alpha-glucanase;
            mutanase;
            endo-(1->3)-alpha-glucanase;
            cariogenase;
            cariogenanase;
            endo-1,3-alpha-D-glucanase;
            1,3(1,3;1,4)-alpha-D-glucan 3-glucanohydrolase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Glycosylases;
            Glycosidases, i.e. enzymes that hydrolyse O- and S-glycosyl compounds
SYSNAME     3-alpha-D-glucan 3-glucanohydrolase
REACTION    Endohydrolysis of (1->3)-alpha-D-glucosidic linkages in isolichenin, pseudonigeran and nigeran
COMMENT     Products from pseudonigeran (1,3-alpha-D-glucan) are nigerose and alpha-D-glucose.
